{
  "texts": [
    "Related work.",
    "There are only a few works that address invariant generation via machine learning.",
    "The work in [32] uses large language models to predict invariants of Java programs.",
    "They specifically trained large language models to predict Daikon [20] generated invariants.",
    "Their evaluation does not consider validity or usefulness of the generated invariants but only concerns whether Daikon invariants can be recovered."
  ]
}